description: Creates a plan. A plan includes the list of resources to be created (when provisioning a new product) or modified (when updating a provisioned product) when the plan is executed. You can create one plan per provisioned product. To create a plan for an existing provisioned product, the product status must be AVAILBLE or TAINTED. To view the resource changes in the change set, use DescribeProvisionedProductPlan. To create or modify the provisioned product, use ExecuteProvisionedProductPlan.
